item.title: What is SQL?
item.description: SQL is a standardized language used to interact with relational [[databases]]. It stands for structured query language (SQL) and defines a standard [[slip-box/programming languages | programming language]] utilized to extract, organize, manage, and manipulate data stored in relational databases.
